Claim your MM3 // KaratDAO featured drop.

This NFT will qualify holders for future token drops, community whitelist, offline events and more.

MM3 is a collection of 6226 3D NFT. The team behide the project @AmethystNFT is the also the team behind Marilyn Monre CGI project, covered by Vogue and partnered with luxury fashion brands including Balenciaga, Fendi, Lanvin, Miu Miu, Thom Browne, etc . 

Partnering with Drepublic, the creator of EIP 3664. MM3 will enable holder “customized” their NFT. The avatar’s Fashion and accessories, and even make up can be interchangeable between NFTs and could be traded separately.
